## Configuration (User‑controllable via UI)

- `inject_opening_stock` : `True` (recommended)  
- `default_margin_percent` : `35.0` (fallback when no purchase history)  
- `opening_stock_buffer` : `50` (extra units to add beyond the deficit)  
- `use_fuzzy_matching` : `True` (for column name mapping)

These can be adjusted in the merger UI.

